						<div class="texto">			
							<div class="title">
								<a name="Solomons"></a> 
								Languages of the Solomons
							</div>
						<p>I have revised the figures for numbers of speakers based on my May 2012 survey, and also taking into account the <a href="https://catalog.ihsn.org/catalog/4595/related-materials" target="_blank">2009 Solomon Islands census</a>.</em></p>
						<p class="smaller"><em>Note</em>: This chart cites only those languages of the Solomon&nbsp;Islands on which I have personally collected data on the field. For a full list of the <strong>74</strong> languages spoken in the Solomons, see <a href="https://glottolog.org/glottolog/language.map.html?country=SB#6/-10.876/165.904" target="_blank">Glottolog</a>. </p>
						
